text: Jadwiga Szoszler-Wilejto (born 22 January 1949) is a retired Polish archer. Szoszler-Wilejto competed at the 1972, 1976 and the 1980 Summer Olympics.Jadwiga Szoszler-WilejtoJadwiga SZOSZLER-WILEJTO == References == Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Polish archers Category:Olympians for Poland
